[[File:Ulysses, 1922.djvu|thumb|600px|center|page=74]]
<br>
==Annotations==
'''''Esprit de corps'''''{{spaces|5}}(''French'') ''Team spirit'', a sense of fellow feeling shared by the members of a particular group or sect (in this case, the female sex).<ref>Gifford (1988) 87.</ref>


