==Annotations==
'''''deus nobis hæc otia fecit'''''{{spaces|5}}(''Latin'') ''a god has made these comforts for us.''<ref>Gifford (1988) 153.<br>Thornton (1968) 127.</ref> The line is a quotation from [[w:Virgil|Virgil's]] collection of pastoral poems, ''[[w:Eclogues|Eclogues]]'' 1:6.<ref>[http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text;jsessionid=900EEF722013E2180C4C6E179F24E180?doc=Perseus%3atext%3a1999.02.0056 ''Eclogues'' 1.]</ref>

