=Vishwas M Byrappa=

A regular user and a very infrequent editor of Wikipedia.

I am a Consultant in [[Astrology]], [[Numerology]], [[Gemmology]], [[Information technology]], [[SEO]], and [[Social marketing]], an Administrator and Editor in New Media Technologies, a Teacher, a blogger and writer.

I am also the Founder, Publisher and Chief Editor of [http://yseeker.ws YSeeker]YSeeker, a Global e-magazine. 

You can find more about me at [http://byrappa.ws Byrappa.ws].


