==Annotations==
'''mavrone'''{{spaces|5}}(''Hiberno-English'') ''Alas!''<ref>[http://archive.org/stream/irishenglishdict011837mbp#page/n111/mode/1up Patrick S. Dinneen, ''Irish-English Dictionary'' 61-62.]</ref> This interjection is an Anglicisation of the Irish expression ''mo bhrón'' (''my sorrow'', ''my grief''). Gifford's annotation is incorrect.

