This is the template for sections of the Web Application Security Guide.
When creating a section for the Guide, you should use it like this:
<pre><nowiki>
{{Web_Application_Security_Guide/Topic|mode={{{1|full}}}
|name={{subst:SUBPAGENAME}}
|intro=
This is a short topic intro

|checklisttitle=Alternative title for checklist (optional)
|checklist=
* one
* two
* three

|rationale=
This explains why one, two, three are so important

}}
</nowiki></pre>

The checklist title is optional, if not given "To prevent this type of attack" will be used.
<code><nowiki>{{subst:SUBPAGENAME}}</nowiki></code> is automatically replaced by the section name.

