==Annotations==
'''''Corpus paradisum'''''{{spaces|5}}(''Latin'') ''Body Paradise.''<ref>Gifford (1988) 304.<br>Thornton (1968) 248.</ref> Bloom has conflated two Latin liturgical expressions he has heard today: ''Corpus'' from St Andrew's Church on Westland Row ([[Annotations_to_James_Joyce's_Ulysses/Lotus_Eaters/077|077.31]]) and ''In Paradisum'' from Paddy Dignam's Burial Service in Prospect Cemetery ([[Annotations_to_James_Joyce's_Ulysses/Hades/100|100.34]]).

