==Annotations==
'''''Faugh a ballagh'''''{{spaces|5}}(''Hiberno-English'') ''Get out of the way!'' An anglicization of the Irish ''Fág an bealach''. In Dineen's ''Irish-English Dictionary'' it is flagged as ''a challenge''.

