==Annotations==
'''''fiat !'''''{{spaces|5}}(''Latin'') ''let there be!''<ref>Gifford (1988) 432.<br>Thornton (1968) 342.</ref> In the Latin [[w:Vulgate|Vulgate]] translation of the [[w:Book of Genesis|Book of Genesis]], God creates light with the words ''fiat lux'' (''let there be light'').<ref>[http://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=Genesis%201&version=VULGATE Genesis 1:3.]</ref>


