==Assumptions== *[[0.999.../Decimal addition and subtraction|Decimal addition and subtraction]] {{stage|0%}} *[[0.999.../Decimal multiplication by 10|Decimal multiplication by 10]] {{stage|0%}}
==Proof== :<math> \begin{align} x &= 0.999\ldots \\ 10 x &= 9.999\ldots \\ 10 x - x &= 9.999\ldots - 0.999\ldots \\ 9 x &= 9 \\ x &= 1 \end{align} </math>
[[Category:0.999...|Proof by multiplication by 10]]

